(326, 2, '2012-12-18 01:48:24', '2012-12-17 14:48:24', 'Setting up of kitchens, training of staff, menu planning, overseeing the day to day running of two large kitchen brigades. Involvement in the marketing of both outlets for local magazines and TV.', 'Q Restaurant & The Mansion Restaurant, Shanghai, China', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'q-restaurant-the-mansion-restaurant-shanghai-china-2', '', '', '2012-12-18 01:48:24', '2012-12-17 14:48:24', '', 0, 'http://chefjustinbentley.com/?post_type=history&#038;p=326', 0, 'history', '', 0),
(327, 2, '2012-12-18 01:49:23', '2012-12-17 14:49:23', 'Day to day duties of running a kitchen within a small business; menu writing, costing of menus and staffing.', 'Rubicon Restaurant, 1 Hat, Erroll St, North Melbourne, Victoria ', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'rubicon-restaurant-1-hat-erroll-st-north-melbourne-victoria-2', '', '', '2012-12-18 01:49:23', '2012-12-17 14:49:23', '', 0, 'http://chefjustinbentley.com/?post_type=history&#038;p=327', 0, 'history', '', 0),
(328, 2, '2012-12-18 01:49:59', '2012-12-17 14:49:59', 'Involved in the initial set up of the kitchen and its brigade; menu planning and infrastructure planning; working closely with operational managers. Responsible for implementing HAACAP systems, WH&amp;S procedures and staff training systems whilst maintaining a high standard of food in a large operation. Overseeing A la Carte, catering and functions with a team of over twenty employees , whilst adhering to and exceeding budget objectives.', 'Plaza Deli Bistro, 71 Eagle St, Brisbane, Queensland ', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'plaza-deli-bistro-71-eagle-st-brisbane-queensland-2', '', '', '2012-12-18 01:49:59', '2012-12-17 14:49:59', '', 0, 'http://chefjustinbentley.com/?post_type=history&#038;p=328', 0, 'history', '', 0),
(329, 2, '2012-12-18 01:50:40', '2012-12-17 14:50:40', 'Working in a variety of establishments around Queensland on a contract chef basis, each establishment being slightly different to the other , and each requiring differing levels of responsibility and skills. Contacts varying from a one off shift to something becoming semipermanent in the hospitality industry. Over that period of time I have developed a good reputation as a contractor and quite a loyal following amongst clients. This also gave me the opportunity to run my own small catering enterprise.', 'Bluestonne Personnel & Zest Recruitment, Queensland ', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'bluestonne-personnel-zest-recruitment-queensland-2', '', '', '2012-12-18 01:50:40', '2012-12-17 14:50:40', '', 0, 'http://chefjustinbentley.com/?post_type=history&#038;p=329', 0, 'history', '', 0),
