(331, 2, '2012-12-18 01:52:08', '2012-12-17 14:52:08', 'Working under the renowned Cheong Liew, ensuring quality control, kitchen procedures are met to the highest standard. Assisting the team to exceed the expectations of the chef and the customers. Maintaining a healthy and happy kitchen morale, whilst mentoring junior staff. Collaborating closely with the chef on demographics and related menu design.', 'Botanical Hotel, Domain Road, South Yarra, Melbourne, Victoria ', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'botanical-hotel-domain-road-south-yarra-melbourne-victoria-2', '', '', '2012-12-18 01:52:08', '2012-12-17 14:52:08', '', 0, 'http://chefjustinbentley.com/?post_type=history&#038;p=331', 0, 'history', '', 0),
(332, 2, '2012-12-18 01:53:24', '2012-12-17 14:53:24', 'I currently work as a catering Sub Contractor through Hospitality Recruitment Companies, as well as private catering events that I mainly receive by word of mouth. The work is extremely hands on &amp; varied I could be doing an ala ''carte Boardroom at a law firm for thirty people by myself. Or I can be working with a large production team preparing and then working the game for large football or concerts. I believe a Chef can gain a lot from doing this sort of work it''s ever changing &amp; one has to be extremely versatile and work smart on your feet so that there is always a positive outcome. That being the customer leaves happy.', 'Bentley Pty Ltd Sole Trader Catering ', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'bentley-pty-ltd-sole-trader-catering-2', '', '', '2012-12-18 02:02:26', '2012-12-17 15:02:26', '', 0, 'http://chefjustinbentley.com/?post_type=history&#038;p=332', 0, 'history', '', 0),
